para: Your Next Tattoo Based on Your Zodiac Sign
Thinking about getting inked? Look to the stars! Your sign says something about your personality, so depending on whether you're a Pisces, Sagittarius, or Virgo, there's an ideal tattoo for you.
Cancer signs receive especially therapeutic benefits from being on or near the ocean, so a water-themed tattoo makes perfect sense.
Leos are cheerful, charismatic, and love to perform. If you love being the star of the show, represent that with actual star tattoos.
Virgos are steadfast and reliable, so show your true nature with an infinity tattoo.
Libras are sociable and make great friends, so your best bet is to get matching tattoos with your BFF or significant other.
Scorpios are charming, passionate, and have a magnetic attraction, so whatever tattoo you get, it should be in a sexy spot that only a lucky few will get the chance to see.
